data.title: Kid's Birthday Party Water Bottle Label
data.meta_description: Personalized and oh-so-cute, these Kid's Birthday Party Water Bottle Label are perfect for keeping kiddo's hydrated and happy as they celebrate. These professionally-printed labels are moisture resistant and made to fit standard 16.9 fl oz water bottles. They are professionally printed with our children's birthday motif, a train design with custom text. Chose your favorite colors or switch up the design and text to make these personalized water bottle labels for baby showers or baby sprinkles!
data.text:
CUSTOMER PROVIDED ART

We can imprint custom logos and artwork! There is no fee if the artwork is submitted in the following format. It can then be used on many of our other items with no additional fee.

Artwork Requirements:

--VECTORIZED art usually from the designer in PDF, EPS, or Ai format (JPGs are never vectorized, not all PDFs are vectorized)

--any text must be OUTLINED

--black and white (no greyscale)

If you do not have access to your art in vector format, we may be able to convert your art for a fee. Alternatively, we can create something custom for you using any of our fonts, designs, or monograms for no additional fee.

Please note that our prices include printing in one color, unless the listings is for a full color item. There are additional fees to print in two colors and subject to design approval.

WANT SOMETHING DIFFERENT?

We specialize in custom orders, and will be happy to create that perfect, custom item just for you. Lets change it up! Colors, fonts, designs, states — we’ve got you covered!

COLOR DISCLAIMER
